node.text:
"If we didn't have bees to do pollination, we'd only be eating wheat and rice." 🐝

Research assistant Rui Gonçalves of the Oxford Bee Lab is studying bee nutrition to ensure UK bee populations can grow.

Discover why Rui's role is one of #101Jobs that change the world ⬇️
https://www.ukri.org/our-work/101-jobs-that-change-the-world/

#TruePlanet #Oxford #OxfordUni #OxfordUniversity #Bees #Beekeeping #BeesNeedsWeek

node.title: Beekeeping is in the top 101 jobs that change the world

Today is #DontStepOnABeeDay! 🐝
.

.
Find out more ➡️ oxfordplanbee.web.ox.ac.uk
